{
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Move Everything",
      "children": [
        {
          "title": "Shortcuts",
          "lines": [
            "Shift+Vol is the",
            "modifier for all ME",
            "shortcuts.",
            "",
            "+Track 1-4: jump to",
            " slot settings",
            "+Menu: Master FX",
            "+Step 2: Global",
            " settings menu",
            "+Step 13: Tools menu",
            "+Jog Click: overtake",
            " module menu",
            "",
            "Shift+Sample:",
            " quantized sampler",
            "Shift+Capture:",
            " skipback last 30s",
            "",
            "Overlay Knobs:",
            " Global Settings >",
            " Display > Overlay",
            " Knobs: +Shift,",
            " +Jog Touch, Off",
            "",
            "Use +Jog Touch or",
            "Off to avoid Shift+",
            "Knob conflicts."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Connecting Tracks",
          "lines": [
            "Set each Move track",
            "MIDI Out to ch 1-4.",
            "",
            "Set each slot Recv",
            "Ch to match (1-4).",
            "",
            "Play the track to",
            "trigger the slot",
            "synth.",
            "",
            "Tip: load an empty",
            "Drum Rack or Sampler",
            "preset on the Move",
            "track to silence the",
            "native sound.",
            "",
            "Pitch bend, mod",
            "wheel, sustain, and",
            "CCs are forwarded",
            "from external MIDI."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Instrument Slots",
          "lines": [
            "4 slots, each with:",
            "MIDI FX > Synth >",
            "Audio FX 1 > FX 2",
            "",
            "Jog wheel scrolls,",
            "click enters, back",
            "goes up a level.",
            "",
            "Navigate to an empty",
            "position and click",
            "to pick a module.",
            "",
            "Shift+Jog Click on",
            "a loaded module to",
            "swap it."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Slot Settings",
          "lines": [
            "Last position in",
            "each slot's menu.",
            "",
            "Knobs 1-8: assign",
            "params from loaded",
            "modules.",
            "",
            "Volume: per-slot",
            "output level.",
            "",
            "Recv Ch: MIDI ch",
            "this slot listens.",
            "",
            "Fwd Ch modes:",
            " Auto: remap to recv",
            " Thru: passthrough",
            " 1-16: force channel",
            "",
            "LFO 1/2: modulation",
            "sources (see LFOs).",
            "",
            "Save/Load slot",
            "presets from here."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "LFOs",
          "lines": [
            "Each slot has 2 LFOs",
            "that modulate any",
            "parameter of any",
            "module in the chain.",
            "",
            "Shapes: Sine, Tri,",
            "Saw, Square, S&H,",
            "Swishy (random walk)",
            "",
            "Sync: free Hz or",
            "tempo-synced (8bar",
            "to 1/32 note).",
            "",
            "Retrigger: resets",
            "phase on first",
            "note-on of a phrase.",
            "",
            "LFOs can target",
            "each other for",
            "complex modulation.",
            "",
            "Master FX also has",
            "2 LFOs (in the",
            "Master FX menu).",
            "",
            "~1/~2 indicators",
            "show active targets",
            "in chain editor."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Sets & Slots",
          "lines": [
            "Each Move Set keeps",
            "its own slots.",
            "",
            "Switching Sets saves",
            "your current slots",
            "and loads the new",
            "Set's slots.",
            "",
            "Changes are local to",
            "the Set. Editing a",
            "synth in one Set",
            "won't affect others.",
            "",
            "Presets are separate:",
            "loading a preset",
            "copies it into the",
            "Set. Tweaks stay in",
            "the Set, not the",
            "preset.",
            "",
            "New Sets start with",
            "empty slots."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Master FX",
          "lines": [
            "Open: Shift+Vol+Menu",
            "",
            "4 audio FX slots",
            "that process the",
            "mixed output of all",
            "instrument slots.",
            "",
            "LFO 1/2 can target",
            "any master FX param.",
            "",
            "Use Shift+Vol+",
            "Step 2 for global",
            "settings (Display,",
            "Audio, Screen Reader",
            "Services, Updates)."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Link Audio",
          "lines": [
            "Requires Move 2.0+.",
            "",
            "Routes Move track",
            "audio through ME FX.",
            "",
            "Setup:",
            "1.Enable Link in",
            "  Move Settings",
            "2.Global Settings",
            "  > Audio > Route",
            "  thru ME: On",
            "",
            "Track N maps to",
            "Slot N audio input.",
            "",
            "When on, Move native",
            "Master FX bypassed.",
            "",
            "Brief play delay",
            "from Link quantum."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Recording",
          "lines": [
            "Quantized Sampler",
            "(Shift+Sample):",
            "",
            "Choose source:",
            " Resample or",
            " Move Input",
            "Choose duration in",
            "bars, or until stop.",
            "Starts on note",
            "event or Play.",
            "Saved to Samples/",
            "Move Everything/.",
            "",
            "Skipback",
            "(Shift+Capture):",
            "",
            "Saves last 30s of",
            "audio. Uses same",
            "source setting as",
            "the sampler."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Overtake Modules",
          "lines": [
            "Full-screen apps",
            "that take over the",
            "display & controls.",
            "",
            "Open overtake menu:",
            " Shift+Vol+Jog Click",
            "",
            "Exit overtake:",
            " Shift+Vol+Jog Click",
            "",
            "After exiting, pad",
            "LEDs may not refresh",
            "- change tracks to",
            "restore them."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Display Mirror",
          "lines": [
            "Stream the OLED to",
            "a web browser.",
            "",
            "Enable in Global",
            "Settings > Display",
            "> Mirror Display.",
            "",
            "Then open:",
            " move.local:7681",
            "",
            "~30 fps, supports",
            "up to 8 clients.",
            "",
            "Off by default.",
            "Persists on reboot."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Screen Reader",
          "lines": [
            "Text-to-speech for",
            "accessibility.",
            "",
            "Toggle on/off:",
            " Global Settings >",
            " Screen Reader",
            " or Shift+Menu",
            "",
            "Settings:",
            " Speed: 0.5x - 6x",
            " Pitch: 80-180 Hz",
            " Volume: 0 - 100%",
            " Debounce: 0-1000ms"
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Tools Menu",
          "lines": [
            "Open: Shift+Vol+",
            "Step 13",
            "",
            "Tools that run",
            "outside the slot",
            "system.",
            "",
            "File Browser: browse",
            "and manage files on",
            "your Move. Play WAV",
            "files to preview.",
            "",
            "More tools available",
            "via Module Store."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "File Browser (Web)",
          "lines": [
            "Web-based file",
            "manager for Move.",
            "",
            "Enable in Settings",
            "> Services > File",
            "Browser.",
            "",
            "Access at:",
            " move.local:404",
            "",
            "Upload, download,",
            "rename, move, and",
            "delete files from",
            "any device on your",
            "network.",
            "",
            "Off by default.",
            "No auth required."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Move Manual",
      "children": [
        {
          "title": "Loading...",
          "lines": [
            "Fetching the Move",
            "manual from",
            "ableton.com.",
            "",
            "Requires an internet",
            "connection."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Notice",
      "children": [
        {
          "title": "Copyright",
          "lines": [
            "Ableton Move Manual",
            "",
            "Copyright 2024",
            "Ableton AG.",
            "All rights reserved.",
            "Made in Germany.",
            "",
            "Manual content",
            "displayed with",
            "permission from",
            "Ableton AG."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Trademark Notice",
          "lines": [
            "Ableton and Move are",
            "trademarks of",
            "Ableton AG.",
            "",
            "Move Everything is",
            "an independent",
            "product and has not",
            "been authorized,",
            "sponsored, or",
            "otherwise approved",
            "by Ableton AG."
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
